  "short_description": "Overcome the challenges of each mini-level in this precision platformer with speedrun and hit-kill mechanics. Every perfectly timed action pushes you forward. Perform your best acrobatics and moves to free the island creatures from the ambitions of Dr. Luiz RockBone!",
