store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660980/extras/56959b730069c49ebe9370f9a4225e80.webm?t=1760643061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660980/extras/56959b730069c49ebe9370f9a4225e80.mp4?t=1760643061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROTECT THE ANIMALS ISLAND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Doctor Luiz RockBone plans to turn Animal Island into a research center for his robots and genetically modified creatures. Even while stuck in training, the animals are plotting ways to drive him out, and you play a crucial role in overcoming challenges and freeing the island from this outsider’s ambitions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660980/extras/57d8652530ebe961db3fef0fc01de7f7.poster.avif?t=1760643061\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660980/extras/57d8652530ebe961db3fef0fc01de7f7.webm?t=1760643061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660980/extras/57d8652530ebe961db3fef0fc01de7f7.mp4?t=1760643061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
